        What do you notice about using this method on the games in <xref ref="T_domstratpractice1"></xref>, <xref ref="T_domstratpractice2"></xref>, and <xref ref="T_domstratpractice3"></xref>? Is the solution an equilibrium pair?
      </p>
    </statement>
  </activity>
  <activity xml:id="A_maxmindomstrat4">
